---
// Premium Local Quote Calculator Page
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Free Grid Audit Calculator</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background: #f4f7f6; color: #1e293b; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .calc-wrapper { max-width: 700px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 30px; background: white; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header-text { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .header-text h1 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #0f172a; font-size: 28px; }
    .header-text p { color: #64748b; font-size: 16px; margin: 0; }
    
    .grid-settings { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 25px; }
    .grid-settings label { font-weight: bold; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .grid-settings select, .grid-settings input { width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px; }

    .appliance-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 15px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;}
    .appliance-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .checkbox-group { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; max-width: 250px;}
    .checkbox-group input { width: 20px; height: 20px; cursor: pointer; accent-color: #0c905c; }
    .model-input { flex-grow: 1; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px; min-width: 200px;}
    
    .calc-btn { background: #0f172a; color: white; border: none; padding: 18px; font-size: 18px; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; width: 100%; transition: all 0.3s ease; margin-top: 20px;}
    .calc-btn:hover { background: #1e293b; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); transform: translateY(-2px); }

    /* Processing Animation */
    #processing { display: none; text-align: center; padding: 40px; }
    .spinner { border: 4px solid #f3f3f3; border-top: 4px solid #0c905c; border-radius: 50%; width: 40px; height: 40px; animation: spin 1s linear infinite; margin: 0 auto 15px auto; }
    @keyframes spin { 0% { transform: rotate(0deg); } 100% { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    /* Results Panel */
    #results-panel { display: none; margin-top: 30px; animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in; }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    .data-box { background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #10bf7a; border-radius: 10px; padding: 25px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 25px;}
    .data-box h3 { color: #0c905c; margin-top: 0; font-size: 22px;}
    
    .lead-capture-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 2px dashed #f59e0b; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="calc-wrapper">
  
  <div id="calculator-step">
    <div class="header-text">
      <h1>⚡ Premium Blackout Load Audit</h1>
      <p>Configure your home's grid specs and appliances to calculate your exact emergency load.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-settings">
      <label>Home Grid Voltage & Connection Phase:</label>
      <select id="grid-voltage">
        <option value="120">Standard US 120V (Most Homes)</option>
        <option value="240">Heavy Duty 240V (Required for Central AC/Well Pumps)</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 10px;">Select Critical Appliances</h3>
      
      <div class="